src:
Jadwal Premier League Pekan Ini, Live di TVRI dan Mola TV
01 Nov 2019, 14:56 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Jadwal pekan ke-11 Premier League musim 2019/2020. Jadwal Manchester United yang akan berjumpa Bournemouth pekan bisa Bolaneters simak pada artikel di bawah ini.
Pekan ke-12 Premier League dibuka dengan duel Bournemouth vs Manchester United. Laga ini digelar pada Sabtu (2/11/2019) malam WIB dan disiarkan di Mola TV.
Manchester United selalu menang dalam tiga laga tandang terakhirnya, termasuk saat mengalahkan Chelsea di Carabao Cup. Setan Merah yang sedang onfire akan berjumpa Bournemouth yang tidak pernah menang dalam empat laga terakhir.
Masih di hari Sabtu, akan ada duel Aston Villa vs Liverpool. Laga ini akan digelar Villa Park pada pukul 22.00 WIB. Aksi pasukan Jurgen Klopp melawan tuan rumah Aston Villa bakal disiarkan langsung TVRI.
text:
This Week's Premier League Schedule, Live on TVRI and Mola TV
Nov 01 2019, 14:56 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Schedule 11th Premier League season 2019/2020. Schedule of Manchester United who will meet Bournemouth last week can see Bolaneters in the article below.
Week 12 of the Premier League opens with a duel between Bournemouth vs Manchester United. This match was held on Saturday (11/02/2019) night WIB and was broadcast on Mola TV.
Manchester United have always won in their last three away games, including when they beat Chelsea in the Carabao Cup. Red Devils who are onfire will meet Bournemouth who have never won in the last four matches.
Still on Saturday, there will be a Aston Villa vs Liverpool duel. This match will be held Villa Park at 22:00 WIB. Jurgen Klopp's action against host Aston Villa will be broadcast live on TVRI.
